				</div>  </div>
				<p class="detail">This is a full-auto player that takes sound quality into consideration as well as high-end models.<br><br>The cartridge uses an MC cartridge that achieves a high output of 2.5 mv with a unique power generation mechanism. It can be directly connected to the MM position without using a dedicated transformer or head amplifier.<br>In addition, the simple structure makes it easy to replace the needle of the MC cartridge, which was difficult to replace with conventional ones.<br><br>The SH rotor system is used for the bearing structure of the drive part, and a newly developed DC servo motor is used for the drive motor.<br><br>The cabinet has adopted a coaxial suspension cabinet with excellent howling resistance.<br><br>A straight arm using carbon graphite is adopted for the tone arm.<br><br>Adopts a full auto mechanism.</p>
